OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FStormont Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,7,Fhas been accused of a "dismissive" and
OL,8,F"flippant" tone towards GPs who say
OL,9,Fthey are facing a funding crisis.
OL,11,FA British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,12,Frepresentative told a Stormont
OL,13,Fcommittee that general practice seems
OL,14,F"not to be a priority" for Mr Nesbitt
OL,15,Fafter he implemented a disputed
OL,16,Ffunding contract.
OL,18,FBut the minister has insisted he was
OL,19,F"honest and accurate" when delivering
OL,20,Fa statement to the Assembly earlier
OL,21,Fthis week.
