OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FOn Monday, Mr Nesbitt said he would
OL,7,Fimpose the 2025/26 General Medical
OL,8,FServices (GMS) contract on GPs, even
OL,9,Fafter it had been rejected in a ballot
OL,10,Fof BMA GPs.
OL,12,FThe minister said there would be a
OL,13,Fpackage of #9.5 million in additional
OL,14,Fcore funding for services for GPs.
