OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FDr Frances O'Hagan, chairwoman of the
OL,7,FBritish Medical Association (BMA)
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland GP committee, said
OL,9,Fshe had intended to use her appearance
OL,10,Fbefore the Stormont Health Committee
OL,11,Fto update MLAs on the contract
OL,12,Fnegotiations.
OL,14,FShe added: "It is safe to say Monday
OL,15,Fchanged all that.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
