OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,F"My colleagues are deeply saddened by
OL,7,Fthe minister's statement on Monday,
OL,8,Fhis dismissive comments and at times
OL,9,Fflippant tone showed just how out of
OL,10,Ftouch he is with his officials about
OL,11,Fthe crisis that is going on in general
OL,12,Fpractice at the minute.
OL,14,F"It is difficult to think of another
OL,15,Fprofession anywhere in the health
OL,16,Fservice that has been spoken about the
OL,17,Fway GPs have been spoken about in both
OL,18,Fthe Assembly and in the media over the
OL,19,Flast few days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
