OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,F"This is the first time that a sitting
OL,7,Fminister in Northern Ireland has
OL,8,Fchosen to impose the GMS contract on
OL,9,FGPs and to say that GPs across the
OL,10,Fcountry are frustrated and angry is a
OL,11,Fcomplete understatement."
OL,13,FDr O'Hagan said there was "obviously a
OL,14,Fhuge gulf between our members and the
OL,15,Fminister".
OL,17,FShe said the BMA had asked for an
OL,18,Fincrease in core funding for surgeries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YOUuD@[OUwD@IO]
