OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FShe added: "Our ask for #80 million is
OL,7,Fto stabilise general practice, keep
OL,8,Fthe lights on, retain and recruit
OL,9,Fadditional staff.
OL,11,F"This represents 1% of the health
OL,12,Fbudget, which is #8 billion.
OL,14,F"It was suggested numerous times, both
OL,15,Fin the media and the Assembly, that
OL,16,Fthis was a blank cheque, which could
OL,17,Fnot be further from the truth.
OL,19,F"It is to stabilise our service."
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU{D@aO]
