OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FDr O'Hagan told the committee: "It is
OL,7,Fpremature for the minister to conclude
OL,8,Fnegotiations as he did.
OL,10,F"As GPs we give you our heartfelt
OL,11,Fassurance that we will keep fighting
OL,12,Ffor our service.
OL,14,F"We will keep fighting for a safe
OL,15,Fservice for our patients, we will keep
OL,16,Ffighting to provide more for patients.
OL,18,F"But to do that, we then have to have
OL,19,Fmore to be able to provide more."
OL,26,@nD@`OUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@aO]
