OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FHe said: "I was setting out to be
OL,7,Fhonest and to be accurate in my
OL,8,Fstatement and that is what I was, I
OL,9,Fwas honest and I was accurate.
OL,11,F"We don't have #80 million. We have a
OL,12,Fshortfall that is now north of #600
OL,13,Fmillion because pay awards add about
OL,14,F#200 million of pressures to the
OL,15,Fbudget.
OL,17,F"There is a problem with access and we
OL,18,Fcannot deny that, we have to face up
OL,19,Fto it and we have to try and deal with
OL,20,Fit."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@DO]
