OL,3,CBMA say GP's are 'not a priority' for
OL,4,CNesbitt after disputed funding contract
OL,6,FHe added: "They (GPs) know that my
OL,7,Fintention is to shift left, which
OL,8,Fmeans we get the focus off the acute
OL,9,Fhospitals into primary care, into
OL,10,Fcommunity care, into social care, into
OL,11,Fprevention and early intervention and
OL,12,Fthat is the thing that GPs do best.
OL,14,F"I think we have got a solid
OL,15,Ffoundation in terms of our joint aims
OL,16,Fand ambitions going forward."
